race.description: Kyneton Horse Of The Year Smokey Warrior Mdn Plt
race.comment: The well-bred FALSTAFFIAN (2) went forward from a wide gate at Sandown-Hillside on debut beaten just 2.4L and impressing. That's proving to be a strong form race, and he's been kept on the fresh side. He's sure to keep improving for a top barn draws inside today. Ready to win and will get every chance. WINSILENCE (6) debuts and is also in good hands. He's had a string of sharp jumpouts and Ben Allen sticks aboard from the latest. Looks to have plenty of talent and is ready to go. TITAHI BAY (9) is third-up off a placing at Benalla and she has more up her sleeve. The inside gate should advantage and she's an each-way hope. Before spelling, AYE VEE AITCH (1) ran a strong relative number in an Open 2 at Flemington. He resumed at Moonee Valley off a jumpout win at Flemington but looked short on fitness. He can improve quickly and Childs rides today from a handy barrier.
